block content
  h2 #{public._data[current.path[0]].title} Me
  div.mod-2thirds.content-text.centered

    :markdown
      <img src="/assets/img/content/me.jpg" alt="" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-942 about-me-image " />

      I'm Ahmed El Gabri you can call me "Gabri", I'm a Web designer/Front-end developer with 5+ years of experience in the field. I like to create Clear, Usable, Fast &amp; Responsive websites/apps. Currently working as a Software Engineer at <a href="http://dubai.dubizzle.com">dubizzle</a>

      My knowledge &amp; skills spans a wide range of topics, Web design, Front-end development, SEO, Responsive Web Design, Performance Optimization, Social Media.

    aside(role="complementary", class="secondary-text row")
      div(id="text-2" class="widget widget_text mod-third")
        h4 My Services
        div.textwidget
          ul
            for service in public._data['about'].services
              li= service




      div(id="text-3", class="widget widget_text mod-third")
        h4 What Iâ€™m not
        div.textwidget
          ul
            li I'm not a logo designer.
            li I'm not a Print designer.
            li I don't do flash..




      div#recent-posts-3.widget.widget_recent_entries.mod-third
        h4 The Blog
        posts = public.blog._data
        data = partial('../_partials/data-loop', { collection: posts })
        ul
          each post, i in data
            - if ( i > 4 ) return
            li
              a(href='/blog/'+post.slug) #{post.title}





    h4 about the site
    p
      :markdown
        This site was built using [harpjs](http://harpjs.com), hosted on [heroku](http://heroku.com) & automatically deployed using [travis CI](https://travis-ci.org). You can check the code on [Github](https://github.com/ahmedelgabri/gabri.me).
